WEBVTT

00:00:05.806 --> 00:00:08.141 line:80%
[♪ pop music playing]

00:00:50.058 --> 00:00:53.770 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:01:04.656 --> 00:01:05.824 line:80%
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

00:01:05.907 --> 00:01:07.784 line:80%
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

00:01:09.619 --> 00:01:13.498 line:80%
[♪ majestic music playing]

00:01:55.957 --> 00:01:57.751 line:80%
[Jeongwoo]
On behalf of the people and the Cabinet,

00:01:58.335 --> 00:01:59.669 line:80%
I offer

00:02:00.462 --> 00:02:02.964 line:80%
my most sincere congratulations
on your union.

00:02:03.924 --> 00:02:05.592 line:80%
[all] Congratulations.

00:02:06.343 --> 00:02:10.388 line:80%
Thank… [coughing]

00:02:13.808 --> 00:02:14.976 line:80%
Seong Huiju.

00:02:16.895 --> 00:02:19.856 line:80%
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

00:02:21.483 --> 00:02:22.484 line:80%
Seong Huiju.

00:02:31.826 --> 00:02:34.245 line:80%
[Huiju breathes heavily]

00:02:35.538 --> 00:02:37.374 line:80%
[guests gasping]

00:02:39.292 --> 00:02:40.460 line:80%
Seong Huiju!

00:02:40.543 --> 00:02:42.712 line:80%
-Huiju.
-Ms. Seong?

00:02:42.796 --> 00:02:44.047 line:80%
Escort His Majesty.

00:02:44.589 --> 00:02:45.715 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:02:47.008 --> 00:02:49.636 line:80%
-Summon a royal physician!
-[Im] Yes, Your Majesty.

00:02:49.719 --> 00:02:51.429 line:80%
We shall leave the palace.

00:02:51.930 --> 00:02:53.181 line:80%
From this moment forth…

00:02:54.683 --> 00:02:58.812 line:80%
anyone who dares to lay a hand
upon my wife shall face my wrath!

00:02:59.312 --> 00:03:00.313 line:80%
Choi Hyeon!

00:03:01.690 --> 00:03:04.109 line:80%
[Lady Choi] Your Royal Highness!

00:03:05.151 --> 00:03:06.152 line:80%
Ms. Seong.

00:03:06.236 --> 00:03:08.238 line:80%
-Send word to her father.
-How did this…

00:03:08.905 --> 00:03:10.740 line:80%
-[I-AN] Choi Hyeon!
-Yes, Your Royal Highness!

00:03:19.207 --> 00:03:20.333 line:80%
Huiju.

00:03:20.917 --> 00:03:21.918 line:80%
Seong Huiju.

00:03:27.924 --> 00:03:31.845 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:03:32.429 --> 00:03:33.763 line:20%
EPISODE 8

00:03:34.472 --> 00:03:37.017 line:20%
[reporter] Can you confirm
whether a plan has been established?

00:03:37.100 --> 00:03:39.310 line:20%
Do you care to comment, Ms. Seong?

00:03:39.394 --> 00:03:41.563 line:20%
Can you tell us anything?

00:03:41.646 --> 00:03:43.398 line:20%
Are you all right, Ms. Seong?

00:03:43.481 --> 00:03:45.275 line:20%
Castle Hospital. As fast as you can.

00:03:46.192 --> 00:03:47.152 line:20%
Seong Huiju.

00:03:47.652 --> 00:03:49.654 line:20%
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

00:03:49.738 --> 00:03:50.905 line:20%
[clamoring]

00:03:53.992 --> 00:03:55.910 line:20%
GRAND PRINCESS SEONG
FAINTS MID-WEDDING

00:03:59.289 --> 00:04:00.707 line:80%
Hold on…

00:04:05.003 --> 00:04:06.337 line:80%
Are you all right, sir?

00:04:06.421 --> 00:04:08.506 line:80%
Contact the Ministry of Transport
for traffic control.

00:04:08.590 --> 00:04:09.591 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:04:09.674 --> 00:04:13.511 line:80%
The escort vehicle must reach
Castle Hospital without any delay.

00:04:13.595 --> 00:04:14.596 line:80%
Understood, sir.

00:04:15.305 --> 00:04:16.598 line:80%
How much of it was broadcast?

00:04:16.681 --> 00:04:18.224 line:80%
It was stopped after her collapse.

00:04:21.352 --> 00:04:24.105 line:80%
Let them know an official statement
will be issued by day's end.

00:04:24.731 --> 00:04:27.275 line:80%
Work with the Royal Guard
on hospital crowd control.

00:04:27.358 --> 00:04:28.359 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:04:45.168 --> 00:04:47.712 line:80%
[sirens wailing]

00:04:51.883 --> 00:04:55.303 line:80%
CASTLE HOSPITAL

00:04:55.386 --> 00:04:56.805 line:80%
[doctor] Patient status?

00:04:56.888 --> 00:04:59.808 line:80%
-Looks serious. Let's check her vitals.
-Yes, Doctor.

00:05:00.433 --> 00:05:01.810 line:80%
[doctor] HR 32, BP 80 systolic.

00:05:02.644 --> 00:05:03.937 line:80%
Breathing is weak.

00:05:05.063 --> 00:05:06.940 line:80%
HR in the thirties. Prepare atropine.

00:05:07.023 --> 00:05:08.191 line:80%
[nurse] Yes, Doctor.

00:05:08.274 --> 00:05:10.485 line:80%
[♪ sorrowful music playing]

00:05:10.568 --> 00:05:12.362 line:80%
Please wait outside, Your Royal Highness.

00:05:14.614 --> 00:05:16.282 line:80%
[doctor] Injecting 0.5 ml of atropine.

00:05:17.659 --> 00:05:19.285 line:80%
[nurse] No response to the atropine.

00:05:19.369 --> 00:05:21.329 line:80%
Her pulse is dropping, Doctor.

00:05:25.375 --> 00:05:26.876 line:80%
[breathes heavily]

00:05:44.894 --> 00:05:47.063 line:80%
You're going to the hospital, right?
We'll go too.

00:05:47.147 --> 00:05:48.606 line:80%
No, all of you will stay put.

00:05:48.690 --> 00:05:50.525 line:80%
How can we? Her Ladyship collapsed.

00:05:50.608 --> 00:05:51.568 line:80%
We need to go and--

00:05:51.651 --> 00:05:55.196 line:80%
Everything Ms. Seong consumed
or wore today must be secured.

00:05:55.697 --> 00:05:57.824 line:80%
Don't dispose of anything.
Keep it exactly as is.

00:05:57.907 --> 00:06:00.368 line:80%
What? But why would we do that?

00:06:00.451 --> 00:06:02.370 line:80%
From this moment on,
no one, myself included,

00:06:03.163 --> 00:06:04.664 line:80%
is to leave the private residence.

00:06:06.791 --> 00:06:09.127 line:80%
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

00:06:29.439 --> 00:06:30.732 line:80%
How did this happen?

00:06:34.152 --> 00:06:35.320 line:80%
[doctor] Your Royal Highness.

00:06:36.696 --> 00:06:39.032 line:80%
The blood test results are back.

00:06:39.991 --> 00:06:41.576 line:80%
[sighs]

00:06:41.659 --> 00:06:44.078 line:80%
[machines beeping]

00:06:44.162 --> 00:06:45.747 line:80%
[doctor] <i>She has digoxin toxicity.</i>

00:06:48.041 --> 00:06:49.042 line:80%
Toxicity?

00:06:50.043 --> 00:06:51.878 line:80%
It's medication used to treat arrhythmias,

00:06:51.961 --> 00:06:53.087 line:80%
but an overdose

00:06:54.172 --> 00:06:55.673 line:80%
can be fatal.

00:06:56.257 --> 00:06:58.176 line:80%
What? Fatal?

00:06:58.259 --> 00:06:59.344 line:80%
What does that mean?

00:06:59.427 --> 00:07:02.889 line:80%
Fortunately, we gave emergency treatment
before it hit peak levels in the blood.

00:07:02.972 --> 00:07:04.933 line:80%
She's being treated with an antidote now.

00:07:05.016 --> 00:07:07.560 line:80%
It'll take a few hours
for her to stabilize.

00:07:07.644 --> 00:07:10.521 line:80%
So she's not dying, right?

00:07:10.605 --> 00:07:12.398 line:80%
-Yes.
-[Taeju] You should've started with that!

00:07:12.482 --> 00:07:14.108 line:80%
Gave me a real heart attack there.

00:07:14.192 --> 00:07:15.777 line:80%
Come on, babe. Don't be like that…

00:07:15.860 --> 00:07:18.488 line:80%
They're leaving already?
Shouldn't they explain more?

00:07:18.571 --> 00:07:19.572 line:80%
[Dayeong] Stop it.

00:07:20.615 --> 00:07:21.658 line:80%
[Taeju sighs]

00:07:24.244 --> 00:07:26.037 line:80%
-I was so shocked.
-[Dayeong] Calm down.

00:07:26.663 --> 00:07:27.997 line:80%
-[gasps]
-[Taeju exclaims]

00:07:28.081 --> 00:07:29.165 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:07:29.249 --> 00:07:30.541 line:80%
[I-AN] Stop!

00:07:32.919 --> 00:07:33.962 line:80%
Step back.

00:07:35.546 --> 00:07:37.590 line:80%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:07:43.972 --> 00:07:47.892 line:80%
Surely, you won't just let this slide.

00:07:49.352 --> 00:07:50.353 line:80%
I have…

00:07:53.523 --> 00:07:55.275 line:80%
no intention of letting this slide.

00:08:11.624 --> 00:08:12.917 line:80%
It was due to drug toxicity.

00:08:13.501 --> 00:08:14.627 line:80%
Toxicity?

00:08:14.711 --> 00:08:15.837 line:80%
The attending physician…

00:08:15.920 --> 00:08:17.797 line:80%
Are you saying
someone tried to poison her?

00:08:22.218 --> 00:08:24.137 line:80%
-Where is the Grand Prince right now?
-Sir.

00:08:24.220 --> 00:08:26.639 line:80%
-But now is not…
-Where is Grand Prince I-AN right now?

00:08:38.276 --> 00:08:39.402 line:80%
I knew…

00:08:42.280 --> 00:08:43.823 line:80%
you would fail to protect her.

00:08:45.116 --> 00:08:46.951 line:80%
She collapsed as soon as
she became your wife.

00:08:47.035 --> 00:08:49.120 line:80%
You couldn't even keep her safe for a day!

00:08:49.203 --> 00:08:51.289 line:80%
[breathes heavily]

00:08:51.372 --> 00:08:52.582 line:80%
That's why I'm here.

00:08:53.875 --> 00:08:54.876 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:08:57.003 --> 00:08:58.004 line:80%
Investigate the palace.

00:08:59.005 --> 00:09:00.006 line:80%
What?

00:09:01.883 --> 00:09:03.885 line:80%
From its staff to the royal family.

00:09:07.138 --> 00:09:08.306 line:80%
Investigate them all.

00:09:09.807 --> 00:09:12.143 line:80%
[scoffs]
Do you realize what you're saying--

00:09:12.226 --> 00:09:13.269 line:80%
I do.

00:09:13.936 --> 00:09:15.063 line:80%
So just do it.

00:09:18.941 --> 00:09:20.026 line:80%
Effective immediately…

00:09:22.653 --> 00:09:24.197 line:80%
I hereby authorize a public inquiry…

00:09:27.492 --> 00:09:28.576 line:80%
into the palace.

00:09:37.877 --> 00:09:38.920 line:80%
You cannot.

00:09:39.754 --> 00:09:41.964 line:80%
The dignity of the Crown will be sullied.

00:09:42.048 --> 00:09:43.466 line:80%
Is that what you seek?

00:09:45.343 --> 00:09:47.303 line:80%
This incident occurred on palace grounds.

00:09:48.721 --> 00:09:52.141 line:80%
This investigation is imperative,
not only for you and His Majesty's safety,

00:09:52.225 --> 00:09:53.643 line:80%
but for the Crown's dignity.

00:09:53.726 --> 00:09:56.604 line:80%
The Royal Protection Branch
can handle that.

00:09:56.687 --> 00:09:58.481 line:80%
An investigation
without privilege is required.

00:10:01.442 --> 00:10:02.693 line:80%
Are you saying…

00:10:04.862 --> 00:10:06.948 line:80%
the royals will be questioned as well?

00:10:08.074 --> 00:10:09.450 line:80%
The Grand Prince authorized it.

00:10:09.534 --> 00:10:11.119 line:80%
I-AN is not the king!

00:10:11.202 --> 00:10:12.537 line:80%
But he serves the Crown…

00:10:13.287 --> 00:10:14.539 line:80%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:10:16.249 --> 00:10:17.500 line:80%
…as its regent.

00:10:22.839 --> 00:10:24.132 line:80%
So, Your Majesty,

00:10:24.715 --> 00:10:28.219 line:80%
please allow the police
to enter the palace.

00:10:49.824 --> 00:10:51.200 line:80%
Before we begin,

00:10:51.826 --> 00:10:54.245 line:80%
we would like to express
our deep concern and regret

00:10:54.328 --> 00:10:57.081 line:80%
over the unfortunate incident
that occurred during the royal wedding.

00:10:58.374 --> 00:11:01.961 line:80%
The Grand Princess was hospitalized
after a medical emergency at the ceremony.

00:11:02.044 --> 00:11:04.922 line:80%
She is presently undergoing treatment
and showing signs of recovery.

00:11:05.006 --> 00:11:08.050 line:80%
You mentioned a medical emergency.
Was there a preexisting condition?

00:11:08.134 --> 00:11:10.219 line:80%
Are external factors being ruled out?

00:11:12.597 --> 00:11:15.391 line:80%
We will take questions
once the statement has concluded.

00:11:19.187 --> 00:11:22.231 line:80%
While the investigation remains ongoing,

00:11:23.024 --> 00:11:24.609 line:80%
concerning factors preclude us

00:11:25.276 --> 00:11:26.861 line:80%
from deeming this a simple accident.

00:11:30.573 --> 00:11:34.494 line:80%
<i>Accordingly, at the Crown's request</i>
<i>and in the interest of the public good,</i>

00:11:34.577 --> 00:11:36.120 line:20%
<i>the government will launch</i>

00:11:36.829 --> 00:11:38.956 line:80%
<i>a public investigation encompassing</i>

00:11:40.041 --> 00:11:42.168 line:80%
<i>the possibility</i>
<i>of intentional harm or terrorism.</i>

00:11:45.254 --> 00:11:49.634 line:80%
<i>The investigation will proceed</i>
<i>with the Ministry of Justice and the NPA,</i>

00:11:49.717 --> 00:11:52.261 line:80%
<i>and will be conducted thoroughly</i>
<i>and transparently.</i>

00:11:53.513 --> 00:11:57.099 line:80%
No political or external pressure
will be permitted to influence

00:11:58.100 --> 00:11:59.769 line:80%
the pursuit of the truth.

00:12:02.772 --> 00:12:04.774 line:80%
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

00:12:06.859 --> 00:12:08.861 line:80%
She didn't eat anything
at the palace that day.

00:12:08.945 --> 00:12:12.156 line:80%
Then, do you remember everything she had
at the private residence?

00:12:12.240 --> 00:12:15.117 line:80%
Uh… She didn't have much of an appetite,

00:12:15.201 --> 00:12:17.161 line:80%
so she only had
half an apple in the morning.

00:12:18.037 --> 00:12:20.414 line:80%
I heard she normally has trouble sleeping.

00:12:20.498 --> 00:12:22.208 line:80%
I wouldn't exactly call it that.

00:12:22.291 --> 00:12:23.751 line:80%
She just doesn't sleep.

00:12:24.669 --> 00:12:25.753 line:80%
She doesn't sleep?

00:12:25.836 --> 00:12:28.464 line:80%
She works through the night in the study.

00:12:29.048 --> 00:12:30.299 line:80%
PERSONAL DETAILS
LEE AREUM

00:12:30.383 --> 00:12:33.052 line:80%
MOTHER: PARK MALJA

00:12:48.609 --> 00:12:51.112 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] <i>No sacred exceptions</i>
<i>in the pursuit of truth.</i>

00:12:51.612 --> 00:12:53.030 line:80%
<i>The palace</i>

00:12:53.823 --> 00:12:55.074 line:80%
<i>will certainly not be exempt.</i>

00:12:56.033 --> 00:12:57.159 line:80%
<i>In the eyes of the law…</i>

00:12:57.243 --> 00:12:58.703 line:80%
Prime Minister Min can be so scary.

00:12:59.495 --> 00:13:00.913 line:80%
It's definitely a bold move.

00:13:01.914 --> 00:13:03.874 line:80%
Isn't this the first time the Crown

00:13:04.667 --> 00:13:06.168 line:80%
is being investigated?

00:13:06.961 --> 00:13:08.045 line:80%
It is.

00:13:08.129 --> 00:13:09.130 line:80%
What?

00:13:09.213 --> 00:13:11.257 line:80%
Are royals untouchable in investigations?

00:13:12.341 --> 00:13:13.718 line:80%
-Inviolable.
-Right.

00:13:15.720 --> 00:13:18.431 line:80%
Not exactly. It's more like…

00:13:19.056 --> 00:13:21.392 line:80%
But are you two ever going home?

00:13:21.976 --> 00:13:24.228 line:80%
Father told us to stay until she wakes up.

00:13:24.312 --> 00:13:25.688 line:80%
Father is worried…

00:13:28.024 --> 00:13:30.026 line:80%
Wait, I think she moved!

00:13:30.109 --> 00:13:31.110 line:80%
What?

00:13:35.031 --> 00:13:38.492 line:80%
[gasps] Huiju, can you hear me?

00:13:44.832 --> 00:13:45.958 line:80%
[Hyeon] Ms. Seong!

00:13:46.792 --> 00:13:48.252 line:80%
It's me! Hyeon!

00:13:51.547 --> 00:13:53.674 line:80%
<i>-Ms. Seong is awake!</i>
-[sighs]

00:13:53.758 --> 00:13:55.259 line:80%
Thank goodness.

00:13:57.470 --> 00:13:58.846 line:80%
Does His Royal Highness know?

00:14:14.779 --> 00:14:16.155 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:14:24.705 --> 00:14:27.750 line:80%
KING HUIJONG THE GREAT
QUEEN UIHYEON

00:14:30.419 --> 00:14:31.754 line:80%
[I-AN] Father…

00:14:34.090 --> 00:14:35.675 line:80%
[whimpering]

00:14:35.758 --> 00:14:37.677 line:80%
How dare you mock

00:14:37.760 --> 00:14:40.513 line:80%
the Crown Prince's authority!

00:14:45.434 --> 00:14:47.228 line:80%
Was I being too greedy again?

00:14:51.941 --> 00:14:52.942 line:80%
Hence…

00:14:55.152 --> 00:14:56.487 line:80%
Is this your wrath,

00:14:58.239 --> 00:14:59.824 line:80%
reminding me not to covet?

00:15:03.661 --> 00:15:04.912 line:80%
How much longer…

00:15:06.664 --> 00:15:07.998 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:15:09.625 --> 00:15:12.253 line:80%
They say she is awake now.

00:15:15.297 --> 00:15:17.675 line:80%
Please slow down,
Your Royal Highness!

00:15:20.928 --> 00:15:22.096 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:15:22.179 --> 00:15:23.472 line:80%
Please slow down.

00:15:24.056 --> 00:15:25.933 line:80%
You will hurt yourself,
Your Royal Highness!

00:15:49.540 --> 00:15:50.750 line:80%
You must be hungry.

00:15:52.918 --> 00:15:53.919 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:16:33.167 --> 00:16:34.418 line:80%
You're okay, right?

00:16:45.805 --> 00:16:47.765 line:80%
Are you okay now?

00:16:50.518 --> 00:16:51.560 line:80%
Are you crying?

00:16:58.651 --> 00:17:00.486 line:80%
[crying]

00:17:06.367 --> 00:17:07.576 line:80%
I thought you were dying.

00:17:08.786 --> 00:17:09.995 line:80%
I thought I lost you.

00:17:12.039 --> 00:17:13.123 line:80%
I really thought…

00:17:21.173 --> 00:17:22.341 line:80%
[I-AN breathes shakily]

00:17:32.935 --> 00:17:34.562 line:80%
[crying]

00:17:37.314 --> 00:17:38.315 line:80%
I'm okay.

00:17:45.614 --> 00:17:46.866 line:80%
But…

00:17:47.533 --> 00:17:49.076 line:80%
why did I collapse?

00:17:58.460 --> 00:17:59.461 line:80%
[music ends]

00:18:02.214 --> 00:18:03.507 line:80%
[door opens]

00:18:16.353 --> 00:18:18.522 line:80%
This will be a joint investigation
between the NPA

00:18:18.606 --> 00:18:20.024 line:80%
and the Royal Protection Branch.

00:18:22.693 --> 00:18:23.861 line:80%
Today, we are questioning…

00:18:27.573 --> 00:18:28.574 line:80%
It must be me.

00:18:39.168 --> 00:18:40.294 line:80%
You stay here.

00:18:40.377 --> 00:18:41.378 line:80%
Me?

00:18:44.590 --> 00:18:45.591 line:80%
Stay with Seong Huiju.

00:18:47.051 --> 00:18:48.052 line:80%
Never leave her side.

00:18:52.973 --> 00:18:54.099 line:80%
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

00:18:54.183 --> 00:18:55.559 line:80%
Leave everything here to me.

00:19:02.650 --> 00:19:03.651 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>What?</i>

00:19:04.234 --> 00:19:05.235 line:80%
Toxicity?

00:19:05.986 --> 00:19:06.987 line:80%
Me?

00:19:08.697 --> 00:19:10.574 line:80%
I barely even take sleeping aids anymore.

00:19:12.242 --> 00:19:14.036 line:80%
[sighs]

00:19:15.120 --> 00:19:19.375 line:80%
[sighs] Just spit it out already.
Why won't anybody tell me anything?

00:19:21.502 --> 00:19:23.128 line:80%
It looks deliberate.

00:19:24.296 --> 00:19:26.048 line:80%
It's not a medication you normally take.

00:19:26.715 --> 00:19:28.842 line:80%
Even if it were,
the amount found in your system…

00:19:29.802 --> 00:19:30.803 line:80%
Ah.

00:19:33.389 --> 00:19:34.515 line:80%
You don't need to worry.

00:19:35.099 --> 00:19:37.059 line:80%
The investigation is underway,
and the government…

00:19:37.142 --> 00:19:38.143 line:80%
And His Royal Highness?

00:19:42.022 --> 00:19:43.565 line:80%
The medication he usually takes…

00:19:44.775 --> 00:19:45.901 line:80%
Did you check those?

00:19:45.985 --> 00:19:50.614 line:80%
SEOUL METROPOLITAN POLICE AGENCY

00:19:56.245 --> 00:19:58.080 line:80%
Did Her Royal Highness mention

00:19:58.163 --> 00:20:00.290 line:80%
any abnormal symptoms prior to collapsing?

00:20:01.959 --> 00:20:02.960 line:80%
No.

00:20:03.043 --> 00:20:05.879 line:80%
Any preexisting conditions or allergies?

00:20:05.963 --> 00:20:10.050 line:80%
Did you not review the report
prepared by my wife's attending physician?

00:20:15.264 --> 00:20:17.558 line:80%
Her blood test results

00:20:18.767 --> 00:20:20.644 line:80%
confirmed digoxin toxicity.

00:20:22.980 --> 00:20:26.108 line:80%
By chance,
are you familiar with this medication?

00:20:26.191 --> 00:20:29.486 line:80%
That's not a question
we agreed on beforehand.

00:20:30.446 --> 00:20:31.613 line:80%
I am familiar.

00:20:32.656 --> 00:20:33.782 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:20:36.452 --> 00:20:37.453 line:80%
It is a medication

00:20:39.371 --> 00:20:40.789 line:80%
I have taken on occasion.

00:20:41.749 --> 00:20:43.333 line:80%
Have you checked or not?

00:20:44.376 --> 00:20:45.377 line:80%
Huiju.

00:20:46.295 --> 00:20:47.963 line:80%
[sighing]

00:20:51.467 --> 00:20:53.010 line:80%
I made a mistake.

00:20:56.513 --> 00:20:58.557 line:80%
<i>The robe was so heavy,</i>
<i>and I tripped.</i>

00:21:00.684 --> 00:21:02.561 line:80%
<i>I fell against the table.</i>

00:21:03.854 --> 00:21:05.773 line:80%
<i>Ms. Do put the goblets back in place.</i>

00:21:05.856 --> 00:21:07.357 line:80%
That's when they were switched.

00:21:08.067 --> 00:21:09.359 line:80%
Our goblets.

00:21:14.990 --> 00:21:16.116 line:80%
Where is he right now?

00:21:19.828 --> 00:21:21.038 line:80%
Huiju.

00:21:21.580 --> 00:21:23.415 line:80%
What are you doing? Calm down!

00:21:23.499 --> 00:21:24.917 line:80%
He's in danger right now!

00:21:27.002 --> 00:21:28.545 line:80%
I believe I was the target.

00:21:30.714 --> 00:21:32.049 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:21:32.132 --> 00:21:33.550 line:80%
May I ask why you think that?

00:21:34.968 --> 00:21:37.596 line:80%
My wife, who doesn't normally
take that medication, survived.

00:21:39.389 --> 00:21:40.766 line:80%
However, had I taken it…

00:21:43.894 --> 00:21:45.062 line:80%
I would have died.

00:21:46.688 --> 00:21:48.065 line:80%
It would've been a fatal dose.

00:21:53.570 --> 00:21:55.197 line:80%
Why are you here? What about…

00:21:55.280 --> 00:21:56.365 line:80%
Please go back inside.

00:21:56.949 --> 00:21:57.950 line:80%
No, I need to--

00:21:58.033 --> 00:21:59.952 line:80%
His Royal Highness commanded that

00:22:00.035 --> 00:22:01.745 line:80%
your safety be placed above all else.

00:22:03.497 --> 00:22:04.498 line:80%
Please go back inside.

00:22:05.707 --> 00:22:06.959 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] You stay here.

00:22:11.630 --> 00:22:12.756 line:80%
I will go…

00:22:14.424 --> 00:22:15.551 line:80%
to His Royal Highness.

00:22:23.851 --> 00:22:25.144 line:80%
[sighs]

00:22:26.436 --> 00:22:28.939 line:80%
[♪ piano playing: "Gymnopédie No.1"]

00:22:59.887 --> 00:23:00.888 line:80%
And Grand Prince I-AN?

00:23:01.388 --> 00:23:04.433 line:80%
He is currently giving a statement
with Mr. Jung in attendance.

00:23:07.769 --> 00:23:08.687 line:80%
At this hour?

00:23:08.770 --> 00:23:11.523 line:80%
They've already started
searching his private residence too.

00:23:12.107 --> 00:23:14.193 line:80%
All items used for the wedding,

00:23:14.276 --> 00:23:16.236 line:80%
even the vehicles that transported them,

00:23:16.737 --> 00:23:18.614 line:80%
are said to be subject
to search and seizure.

00:23:21.325 --> 00:23:23.410 line:80%
Take care of any potential issues early.

00:23:23.952 --> 00:23:25.245 line:80%
Make it clean, no loose ends.

00:23:25.829 --> 00:23:27.122 line:80%
Do not worry, Your Majesty.

00:23:27.206 --> 00:23:29.041 line:80%
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

00:23:42.346 --> 00:23:43.388 line:80%
Sir.

00:23:43.472 --> 00:23:45.432 line:80%
These are the personnel files
you asked for.

00:23:47.059 --> 00:23:50.604 line:80%
They include the attendants' family ties,
changes in assets, and their whereabouts

00:23:50.687 --> 00:23:52.481 line:80%
and call history over the past month.

00:23:53.023 --> 00:23:54.608 line:80%
And the Grand Prince's medical records?

00:23:56.985 --> 00:23:58.445 line:80%
Everyone who accessed it recently

00:23:58.528 --> 00:24:00.364 line:80%
are physicians
at the Royal Seoul Hospital.

00:24:00.447 --> 00:24:01.823 line:80%
Less than ten total.

00:24:01.907 --> 00:24:04.576 line:80%
Is Her Majesty's brother one of the ten?

00:24:04.660 --> 00:24:06.078 line:80%
Yes, sir. Both of them.

00:24:08.997 --> 00:24:11.792 line:80%
When will the Royal Seoul Hospital,
including them, be investigated?

00:24:12.376 --> 00:24:13.627 line:80%
Well…

00:24:13.710 --> 00:24:14.753 line:80%
Start now.

00:24:17.631 --> 00:24:18.715 line:80%
Yes, sir. Understood.

00:24:22.094 --> 00:24:23.095 line:80%
[sighs]

00:24:26.181 --> 00:24:27.516 line:80%
[music ends]

00:24:35.107 --> 00:24:37.359 line:80%
You should head to the palace
when you're done here.

00:24:38.277 --> 00:24:39.778 line:80%
My wife is at the hospital.

00:24:39.861 --> 00:24:42.281 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] When the day breaks,
she will be escorted to the palace.

00:24:42.364 --> 00:24:44.866 line:80%
The palace will be safest for both of you.

00:24:49.288 --> 00:24:52.291 line:80%
It is also the place
where you hold complete control.

00:24:53.125 --> 00:24:54.126 line:80%
I shall handle

00:24:55.085 --> 00:24:56.295 line:80%
all the matters beyond it.

00:24:57.254 --> 00:24:59.214 line:80%
[♪ dramatic music playing]

00:25:02.342 --> 00:25:04.428 line:80%
Your Royal Highness,
are you doing all right?

00:25:04.511 --> 00:25:06.638 line:80%
The Grand Princess shall reside
in Anhwadang Hall.

00:25:06.722 --> 00:25:09.182 line:80%
Pardon? But the private residence is
where she must--

00:25:09.266 --> 00:25:11.643 line:80%
I will also assign new palace attendants.

00:25:12.894 --> 00:25:15.105 line:80%
Royal security will also be reinforced.

00:25:15.188 --> 00:25:16.231 line:80%
Prepare accordingly.

00:25:16.315 --> 00:25:17.316 line:80%
Pardon?

00:25:20.694 --> 00:25:22.112 line:80%
What we need is a fortress.

00:25:32.873 --> 00:25:34.666 line:80%
A CATASTROPHIC DEBUT AT COURT

00:25:35.334 --> 00:25:36.460 line:80%
[Huiju sighs]

00:25:37.044 --> 00:25:38.670 line:80%
Talk about a main character moment.

00:25:43.550 --> 00:25:46.094 line:80%
[sighing]

00:25:46.970 --> 00:25:48.805 line:80%
The sun's up. It's already morning.

00:25:48.889 --> 00:25:50.640 line:80%
-[phone chimes]
-Hmm?

00:25:50.724 --> 00:25:52.851 line:20%
PRINCE:
THE QUESTIONING WENT WELL

00:25:52.934 --> 00:25:53.852 line:20%
PRINCE

00:25:55.937 --> 00:25:58.690 line:80%
-[I-AN] <i>Did you not sleep?</i>
-Where are you? Are you okay?

00:25:59.608 --> 00:26:02.069 line:80%
Wait. Is Jeongwoo there with you?

00:26:02.694 --> 00:26:03.695 line:80%
<i>No, he's not.</i>

00:26:04.196 --> 00:26:07.282 line:80%
I mean, why would you leave
your aide here?

00:26:07.366 --> 00:26:09.201 line:80%
There are plenty of royal guards as it is.

00:26:09.951 --> 00:26:11.328 line:80%
That should be a fun car ride.

00:26:11.953 --> 00:26:12.954 line:80%
What?

00:26:13.538 --> 00:26:15.082 line:80%
Come to the palace. Both of you.

00:26:18.835 --> 00:26:23.173 line:80%
CASTLE HOSPITAL

00:26:23.256 --> 00:26:25.884 line:80%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:26:35.811 --> 00:26:36.978 line:80%
[Dayeong] <i>Huiju.</i>

00:26:38.939 --> 00:26:40.190 line:80%
[sighs]

00:26:42.776 --> 00:26:45.320 line:80%
-Hello, Aide Choi.
-Hello. You're back.

00:26:45.404 --> 00:26:47.030 line:80%
Why are you even back?

00:26:47.114 --> 00:26:48.990 line:80%
I heard you're off to the palace soon.

00:26:50.492 --> 00:26:52.619 line:80%
Is she really okay to be discharged now?

00:26:52.702 --> 00:26:56.123 line:80%
Yes. The detox is complete,
so there shouldn't be any issues.

00:26:56.206 --> 00:26:59.835 line:80%
Still, it would be best to keep her
on ECG monitoring

00:26:59.918 --> 00:27:02.212 line:80%
at the palace for about two more days.

00:27:02.295 --> 00:27:03.338 line:80%
I see. Thank you.

00:27:03.422 --> 00:27:04.464 line:80%
-Thank you, sir.
-Sure.

00:27:06.967 --> 00:27:08.677 line:80%
The palace has been notified, right?

00:27:09.386 --> 00:27:10.846 line:80%
Yes. Anhwadang Hall already has--

00:27:10.929 --> 00:27:12.305 line:80%
[Huiju] Excuse me.

00:27:12.889 --> 00:27:13.890 line:80%
Dayeong.

00:27:14.516 --> 00:27:16.226 line:80%
Father sent me.

00:27:16.309 --> 00:27:17.686 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:27:18.270 --> 00:27:20.897 line:80%
His Royal Highness also asked me for help.

00:27:23.024 --> 00:27:24.109 line:80%
He did?

00:27:24.192 --> 00:27:25.735 line:80%
[♪ whimsical music playing]

00:27:25.819 --> 00:27:27.904 line:80%
Your right-hand woman too.

00:27:31.283 --> 00:27:33.535 line:80%
CASTLE HOSPITAL

00:27:34.953 --> 00:27:38.623 line:80%
Gosh, you look so pretty
even when you're sick.

00:27:40.709 --> 00:27:42.752 line:80%
Do I really look very pretty today too?

00:27:43.628 --> 00:27:45.297 line:80%
Yes. Always very pretty, all the time.

00:27:45.881 --> 00:27:47.507 line:80%
Geez, I can't believe this.

00:27:47.591 --> 00:27:49.468 line:80%
Couldn't my beauty
have taken a break today?

00:27:50.719 --> 00:27:52.095 line:80%
Do you have a cushion on you?

00:27:52.179 --> 00:27:53.763 line:80%
-Cushion?
-This cushion.

00:27:58.810 --> 00:28:01.354 line:80%
[sighs] You weren't lying.

00:28:02.689 --> 00:28:03.690 line:80%
How exhausting.

00:28:06.193 --> 00:28:07.652 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:28:07.736 --> 00:28:10.864 line:80%
The whole country saw me collapse live.

00:28:10.947 --> 00:28:12.824 line:80%
I can't be this pretty
when I'm discharged.

00:28:13.575 --> 00:28:15.243 line:80%
I checked the news early this morning.

00:28:15.327 --> 00:28:18.288 line:80%
Online trolls are spreading some bullshit
about me being a jinx

00:28:18.371 --> 00:28:20.332 line:80%
who brought bad luck
to the palace or whatever.

00:28:21.666 --> 00:28:22.876 line:80%
[inhales sharply] Ah.

00:28:23.877 --> 00:28:27.297 line:80%
The last time Taeju was in hot water,
the sympathy card worked best too.

00:28:27.380 --> 00:28:28.381 line:80%
Let me.

00:28:29.925 --> 00:28:31.343 line:80%
Hmm.

00:28:32.761 --> 00:28:33.887 line:80%
Huiju.

00:28:33.970 --> 00:28:36.056 line:80%
Try putting on a pitiful expression.

00:28:36.139 --> 00:28:37.140 line:80%
Like this.

00:28:39.017 --> 00:28:40.936 line:80%
Why go that far?

00:28:41.811 --> 00:28:43.021 line:80%
[Dayeong] Why not? Just try it.

00:28:43.104 --> 00:28:45.273 line:80%
-You might as well go all out.
-Mm-mmm.

00:28:45.357 --> 00:28:46.733 line:80%
-There she comes!
-Here she is!

00:28:46.816 --> 00:28:48.860 line:80%
[♪ pop music playing]

00:28:49.528 --> 00:28:52.322 line:80%
The Prime Minister's office suggested
a possible targeted attack.

00:28:52.405 --> 00:28:54.533 line:80%
Can you give us
an update on your condition?

00:28:54.616 --> 00:28:56.993 line:80%
Why were you not treated
at the Royal Seoul Hospital?

00:28:57.077 --> 00:28:59.162 line:80%
-[coughing]
-Hold on. My goodness.

00:29:08.129 --> 00:29:09.589 line:80%
Careful, Your Royal Highness.

00:29:09.673 --> 00:29:12.342 line:80%
[clamoring]

00:29:21.935 --> 00:29:23.979 line:80%
[coughing]

00:29:28.733 --> 00:29:29.734 line:80%
[Hyejeong] <i>All right.</i>

00:29:29.818 --> 00:29:32.654 line:80%
It might feel a bit awkward,
since this isn't our usual approach.

00:29:32.737 --> 00:29:35.323 line:80%
We're going for weak and feeble,
not tough and strong.

00:29:35.407 --> 00:29:37.325 line:80%
But it shouldn't be that difficult.

00:29:37.826 --> 00:29:41.162 line:80%
As the CEO of Castle Beauty,
she was a rich conglomerate heiress.

00:29:41.246 --> 00:29:44.249 line:80%
But at the palace,
she's just a lowborn outcast.

00:29:44.332 --> 00:29:45.750 line:80%
A CATASTROPHIC DEBUT AT COURT

00:29:45.834 --> 00:29:48.712 line:80%
Make her out to be a tragic heroine.

00:29:48.795 --> 00:29:50.547 line:80%
One that you'd totally want to root for.

00:29:50.630 --> 00:29:51.965 line:80%
[passerby 1] What's going on?

00:29:52.048 --> 00:29:53.466 line:80%
VISIBLY GAUNT,
COUGHING CONTINUOUSLY

00:29:53.550 --> 00:29:55.135 line:80%
[passerby 2]
<i>My friend who works at the palace</i>

00:29:55.218 --> 00:29:56.595 line:80%
<i>told me she collapsed there once before.</i>

00:29:56.678 --> 00:29:58.013 line:80%
<i>The Queen Mother is so hard on her.</i>

00:29:58.096 --> 00:30:00.140 line:80%
[passerby 3]
<i>If she didn't marry into the royal family,</i>

00:30:00.223 --> 00:30:01.850 line:80%
<i>she'd be living large as an heiress.</i>

00:30:01.933 --> 00:30:03.226 line:80%
<i>I feel bad for her.</i>

00:30:03.310 --> 00:30:05.770 line:80%
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

00:30:16.448 --> 00:30:17.657 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:30:21.077 --> 00:30:22.203 line:80%
[door opens]

00:30:27.292 --> 00:30:28.293 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:30:28.376 --> 00:30:31.630 line:80%
The Royal Secretariat submitted
this month's official schedule.

00:30:34.215 --> 00:30:36.384 line:80%
It seems the duties
assigned to the Grand Princess

00:30:36.468 --> 00:30:37.844 line:80%
are being redistributed.

00:30:38.678 --> 00:30:42.223 line:80%
They are wondering how much Your Majesty
is willing to take on in her stead…

00:30:45.602 --> 00:30:47.437 line:80%
Inform them I shall assume all her duties.

00:30:47.520 --> 00:30:50.482 line:80%
Pardon? All of them?

00:30:52.150 --> 00:30:54.319 line:80%
We must present ourselves
as sisters-in-law

00:30:54.402 --> 00:30:56.154 line:80%
in perfect accord.

00:31:23.473 --> 00:31:25.183 line:80%
How shocked you must have been.

00:31:30.730 --> 00:31:32.941 line:80%
I hear you will be staying
at the palace for now.

00:31:34.192 --> 00:31:36.861 line:80%
As it happens,
I have just ordered that all duties

00:31:36.945 --> 00:31:39.656 line:80%
assigned to you be transferred to me.

00:31:39.739 --> 00:31:41.783 line:80%
Just attend to your recovery.

00:31:41.866 --> 00:31:45.286 line:80%
[chuckles] It appears
Her Royal Highness is feeling faint.

00:31:45.370 --> 00:31:47.580 line:80%
[Hyeon] Goodness.
Are you okay, Your Royal Highness?

00:31:48.873 --> 00:31:50.625 line:80%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:31:50.709 --> 00:31:52.502 line:80%
Your Majesty, Her Royal Highness--

00:31:52.585 --> 00:31:53.586 line:80%
I heard.

00:31:55.880 --> 00:31:57.132 line:80%
Please make your way inside.

00:32:02.262 --> 00:32:04.556 line:80%
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

00:32:21.656 --> 00:32:22.949 line:80%
[♪ melancholy music playing]

00:32:23.032 --> 00:32:24.784 line:80%
[official] <i>The Queen Mother shall lend</i>

00:32:24.868 --> 00:32:26.995 line:80%
her cooperation in preparing

00:32:27.495 --> 00:32:29.998 line:80%
a statement today,
and His Majesty by tomorrow.

00:32:30.665 --> 00:32:31.875 line:80%
However,

00:32:32.375 --> 00:32:33.710 line:80%
Her Majesty has indicated

00:32:34.753 --> 00:32:37.005 line:80%
she will be present
for His Majesty's statement.

00:32:49.642 --> 00:32:50.643 line:80%
The request is denied.

00:32:52.479 --> 00:32:53.480 line:80%
Her Majesty

00:32:54.147 --> 00:32:56.608 line:80%
holds the dignity of the palace above all.

00:32:57.275 --> 00:32:59.110 line:80%
I do not intend to take issue with that.

00:33:00.153 --> 00:33:02.572 line:80%
However, I wish to ease
His Majesty's burden as much as possible.

00:33:04.491 --> 00:33:05.742 line:80%
But His Majesty is--

00:33:05.825 --> 00:33:07.327 line:80%
He should be capable of that much.

00:33:10.622 --> 00:33:13.792 line:80%
He is the sovereign
of a nation, after all.

00:33:17.629 --> 00:33:18.630 line:80%
[door closes]

00:33:20.757 --> 00:33:21.758 line:80%
Your Majesty?

00:33:22.383 --> 00:33:23.510 line:80%
Aunt.

00:33:26.137 --> 00:33:27.931 line:80%
Are you feeling all right?

00:33:28.515 --> 00:33:30.600 line:80%
I heard you were sick.

00:33:30.683 --> 00:33:32.310 line:80%
Ah, were you worried about me?

00:33:33.937 --> 00:33:36.231 line:80%
I heard the police

00:33:36.314 --> 00:33:39.651 line:80%
are coming into the palace
because you fainted.

00:33:40.777 --> 00:33:44.572 line:80%
[chuckles] It is because they are curious.

00:33:45.156 --> 00:33:47.075 line:80%
They want to know
if indigestion was to blame

00:33:47.158 --> 00:33:48.785 line:80%
or if someone pushed me.

00:33:48.868 --> 00:33:51.329 line:80%
No one pushed you.

00:33:51.412 --> 00:33:53.706 line:80%
[chuckles] Yes.

00:33:53.790 --> 00:33:56.584 line:80%
They are investigating
because they want to know those things.

00:33:58.545 --> 00:34:00.505 line:80%
Aide Choi, they are asking you
questions too, right?

00:34:00.588 --> 00:34:03.091 line:80%
Pardon? Yes, of course.

00:34:03.174 --> 00:34:05.927 line:80%
They are asking me. Court Lady Choi too.

00:34:06.010 --> 00:34:07.011 line:80%
You too, right?

00:34:07.095 --> 00:34:09.889 line:80%
Even the street cats
will be questioned, Your Majesty.

00:34:09.973 --> 00:34:13.017 line:80%
Might you be a dummy?

00:34:13.101 --> 00:34:14.102 line:80%
Pardon?

00:34:14.185 --> 00:34:16.312 line:80%
Cats cannot talk.

00:34:16.396 --> 00:34:19.440 line:80%
-[laughs]
-[laughing]

00:34:23.945 --> 00:34:25.864 line:80%
-Your Royal Highness.
-Uncle!

00:34:33.121 --> 00:34:34.163 line:80%
Uncle.

00:34:37.166 --> 00:34:38.167 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:34:46.551 --> 00:34:49.971 line:80%
[♪ uplifting music playing]

00:35:17.081 --> 00:35:19.208 line:80%
-[gasps]
-[gasps] Ms. Do!

00:35:19.292 --> 00:35:20.710 line:80%
-Hello.
-Wait.

00:35:21.210 --> 00:35:23.588 line:80%
Now, you're Aide Do
of the Grand Prince's office.

00:35:25.089 --> 00:35:26.090 line:80%
Right.

00:35:27.008 --> 00:35:28.551 line:80%
Hello.

00:35:28.635 --> 00:35:29.761 line:80%
Regarding Ms. Seong…

00:35:32.347 --> 00:35:33.640 line:80%
It's just refusing to stick.

00:35:33.723 --> 00:35:35.600 line:80%
[chuckles] I know, right?

00:35:36.434 --> 00:35:39.729 line:80%
Thank you for helping out
with the discharge of Her Royal Highness.

00:35:39.812 --> 00:35:42.774 line:80%
It was nothing. We're family, after all.

00:35:42.857 --> 00:35:44.609 line:80%
Where is Her Royal Highness?

00:35:46.527 --> 00:35:47.528 line:80%
[music ends]

00:35:49.030 --> 00:35:51.699 line:80%
[I-AN] My wife still does not know
her way around the palace.

00:35:51.783 --> 00:35:53.368 line:80%
She will require the most attentive care.

00:35:53.868 --> 00:35:55.620 line:80%
I will bear that in mind,
Your Royal Highness.

00:35:56.162 --> 00:35:59.999 line:80%
Until new palace attendants are assigned,
the only people permitted in her presence

00:36:00.083 --> 00:36:04.087 line:80%
shall be you, Aide Choi,
Aide Do, and Ms. Han Dayeong.

00:36:04.170 --> 00:36:07.131 line:80%
-Yes, Your Royal Highness.
-Furthermore, my wife

00:36:07.215 --> 00:36:09.050 line:80%
-has trouble sleeping--
-Your Royal Highness.

00:36:10.426 --> 00:36:12.011 line:80%
Yes? Are you feeling unwell?

00:36:12.595 --> 00:36:13.596 line:80%
I'd like…

00:36:14.681 --> 00:36:16.349 line:80%
some alone time with you.

00:36:19.644 --> 00:36:21.312 line:80%
[echoing] Is that not allowed?

00:36:22.730 --> 00:36:23.731 line:80%
[stammers]

00:36:24.399 --> 00:36:25.400 line:80%
No?

00:36:27.652 --> 00:36:28.653 line:80%
Right.

00:36:29.237 --> 00:36:30.238 line:80%
Leave us.

00:36:31.155 --> 00:36:32.240 line:80%
Leave!

00:36:32.323 --> 00:36:33.324 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:36:34.283 --> 00:36:37.078 line:80%
[♪ light music playing]

00:36:47.005 --> 00:36:48.339 line:80%
We must be understanding.

00:36:48.423 --> 00:36:49.799 line:80%
They are newlyweds, after all.

00:36:52.135 --> 00:36:53.136 line:80%
Newlyweds.

00:36:53.886 --> 00:36:55.138 line:80%
[sighs]

00:36:55.722 --> 00:36:57.140 line:80%
-My goodness.
-[laughs]

00:36:59.934 --> 00:37:01.144 line:80%
[music ends]

00:37:09.861 --> 00:37:10.862 line:80%
[sighs]

00:37:10.945 --> 00:37:12.780 line:80%
Is this why you wanted to be alone?

00:37:14.365 --> 00:37:15.700 line:80%
You know,

00:37:16.242 --> 00:37:18.786 line:80%
I really thought I could remain unfazed
by my new title.

00:37:20.955 --> 00:37:23.499 line:80%
But now that everyone is calling me,
"Your Royal Highness"…

00:37:26.002 --> 00:37:27.503 line:80%
I can't help but be a bit cautious.

00:37:28.629 --> 00:37:31.966 line:80%
It feels like I should be
the epitome of elegance every second.

00:37:32.759 --> 00:37:35.803 line:80%
Everyone is monitoring me,
both at the hospital and here.

00:37:35.887 --> 00:37:37.221 line:80%
Not monitoring. Protecting.

00:37:42.477 --> 00:37:45.021 line:80%
And the questioning? Did it go well?

00:37:46.773 --> 00:37:49.025 line:80%
[sighs] Well… I almost fell asleep.

00:37:50.485 --> 00:37:51.486 line:80%
But it was fine.

00:37:56.616 --> 00:38:00.244 line:80%
Listen, I've been thinking about it…

00:38:02.538 --> 00:38:06.000 line:80%
And I think you're the one
who needs protection,

00:38:06.918 --> 00:38:08.544 line:80%
not me.

00:38:13.424 --> 00:38:14.467 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:38:15.343 --> 00:38:16.469 line:80%
I know.

00:38:17.011 --> 00:38:18.012 line:80%
What?

00:38:19.180 --> 00:38:20.765 line:80%
How are you so calm?

00:38:20.848 --> 00:38:22.892 line:80%
-Because I'm relieved.
-About what?

00:38:22.975 --> 00:38:25.728 line:80%
I would be terrified right now
if you were the target.

00:38:27.438 --> 00:38:28.523 line:80%
But if I'm the target…

00:38:30.691 --> 00:38:31.692 line:80%
I thank the heavens.

00:38:34.320 --> 00:38:35.947 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:38:43.162 --> 00:38:44.372 line:80%
-[grunts]
-Ah!

00:38:47.166 --> 00:38:48.417 line:80%
Have you lost your mind?

00:38:48.501 --> 00:38:51.379 line:80%
And if you make me a widow? What then?

00:38:51.462 --> 00:38:53.631 line:80%
Why are you thanking the heavens?

00:38:53.714 --> 00:38:56.676 line:80%
You expect me to live
in the palace alone? Without you?

00:38:56.759 --> 00:38:57.760 line:80%
Stop it already.

00:39:01.931 --> 00:39:04.100 line:80%
If something terrible happens to you…

00:39:09.355 --> 00:39:10.815 line:80%
I can't even get divorced.

00:39:15.820 --> 00:39:17.029 line:80%
[laughs]

00:39:18.114 --> 00:39:19.115 line:80%
You think this is funny?

00:39:19.198 --> 00:39:21.367 line:80%
You have a dramatic way
of expressing concern.

00:39:28.166 --> 00:39:29.250 line:80%
Just lie down.

00:39:36.007 --> 00:39:37.091 line:80%
You're a royal now.

00:39:38.217 --> 00:39:39.510 line:80%
So what?

00:39:40.178 --> 00:39:42.221 line:80%
Do I have to keep quiet
even if I'm being targeted?

00:39:44.891 --> 00:39:46.851 line:80%
You must exercise your royal powers.

00:39:49.020 --> 00:39:50.021 line:80%
Which are?

00:39:52.064 --> 00:39:53.482 line:80%
INVITATION TO ROYAL ACADEMY
80TH ANNIVERSARY

00:39:53.566 --> 00:39:54.567 line:80%
SCHEDULE OF PUBLIC EVENTS

00:39:57.695 --> 00:39:59.989 line:80%
-[Hyejeong] Fashion Week.
-[Hyeon] Oh, Fashion Week?

00:40:00.072 --> 00:40:03.034 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>In grand assemblies,</i>
<i>you shall embody the pride of the realm.</i>

00:40:08.289 --> 00:40:09.290 line:80%
[Hyeon] Right.

00:40:13.044 --> 00:40:14.212 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>And in places of honor,</i>

00:40:15.046 --> 00:40:16.422 line:80%
<i>you shall embody its glory…</i>

00:40:18.382 --> 00:40:19.592 line:80%
to be loved?

00:40:20.843 --> 00:40:21.844 line:80%
Hmm?

00:40:21.928 --> 00:40:25.181 line:80%
Who would dare harm a person who is
the nation's pride and glory?

00:40:27.600 --> 00:40:30.561 line:80%
Does that belief embolden you
to be so reckless?

00:40:30.645 --> 00:40:32.730 line:80%
Because you are
"the nation's pride and glory"?

00:40:33.689 --> 00:40:34.690 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:40:35.733 --> 00:40:37.318 line:80%
I was never reckless.

00:40:37.401 --> 00:40:38.402 line:80%
I just sometimes

00:40:39.362 --> 00:40:40.404 line:80%
do what I want to do.

00:40:42.907 --> 00:40:43.991 line:80%
[gasps] Oh.

00:40:44.075 --> 00:40:45.826 line:80%
-I don't know what to do.
-About what?

00:40:45.910 --> 00:40:46.994 line:80%
Earlier, the Queen Mother

00:40:47.495 --> 00:40:49.705 line:80%
said she'd perform
my public duties on my behalf.

00:40:50.289 --> 00:40:51.749 line:80%
[chuckles] Oh, that?

00:40:52.375 --> 00:40:53.626 line:80%
It's fine.

00:40:56.337 --> 00:40:57.338 line:80%
I denied her request.

00:41:05.012 --> 00:41:06.931 line:80%
There is to be no change to my schedule?

00:41:07.014 --> 00:41:08.349 line:80%
His Royal Highness

00:41:09.100 --> 00:41:11.727 line:80%
stated that all public duties
will be duly fulfilled,

00:41:13.020 --> 00:41:15.398 line:80%
and that Your Majesty does not need

00:41:15.481 --> 00:41:16.565 line:80%
to worry herself.

00:41:16.649 --> 00:41:17.650 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:41:20.069 --> 00:41:22.655 line:80%
It appears the Grand Prince refuses
to exercise any caution.

00:41:27.493 --> 00:41:29.954 line:80%
[court lady] Your Majesty,
Lord INPYEONG has arrived.

00:41:31.747 --> 00:41:34.333 line:80%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:41:38.379 --> 00:41:39.505 line:80%
Show him in.

00:41:40.673 --> 00:41:42.341 line:80%
[sighs]

00:41:44.385 --> 00:41:45.594 line:80%
[sighs]

00:41:49.515 --> 00:41:52.810 line:80%
You should refrain from visiting
the palace for the time being.

00:41:59.400 --> 00:42:02.653 line:80%
I fear it may give rise
to unnecessary misunderstanding.

00:42:07.366 --> 00:42:08.451 line:80%
Your Majesty

00:42:09.118 --> 00:42:11.078 line:80%
would do well to exercise some caution.

00:42:13.122 --> 00:42:14.457 line:80%
Do you care to elaborate?

00:42:16.000 --> 00:42:18.085 line:80%
I meant nothing by it.

00:42:18.586 --> 00:42:19.587 line:80%
I…

00:42:21.464 --> 00:42:23.215 line:80%
only fear it may give rise

00:42:24.258 --> 00:42:25.885 line:80%
to unnecessary misunderstanding.

00:42:43.235 --> 00:42:44.945 line:80%
[music fades]

00:42:45.029 --> 00:42:46.030 line:80%
[door closes]

00:42:48.699 --> 00:42:49.700 line:80%
Sir.

00:42:57.917 --> 00:43:01.170 line:80%
They discovered traces of digoxin
in a goblet used in the wedding rites.

00:43:03.547 --> 00:43:04.715 line:80%
FORENSIC EXAMINATION REPORT

00:43:04.799 --> 00:43:06.634 line:80%
PHOTO 1: GOBLET CONTAINING
TRACES OF DIGOXIN

00:43:06.717 --> 00:43:07.927 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>They were switched then.</i>

00:43:08.552 --> 00:43:09.762 line:80%
<i>Our goblets.</i>

00:43:11.180 --> 00:43:12.765 line:80%
The medication he usually takes…

00:43:13.933 --> 00:43:15.226 line:80%
Did you check those?

00:43:16.560 --> 00:43:18.687 line:80%
What are you doing? Calm down!

00:43:18.771 --> 00:43:20.398 line:80%
He's in danger right now!

00:43:21.690 --> 00:43:23.234 line:80%
-[knocks on door]
-[door opens]

00:43:25.319 --> 00:43:27.238 line:80%
[assistant]
Sir, Ms. Lee Areum has arrived.

00:43:46.424 --> 00:43:48.759 line:80%
[Huiju] What? You're really that swamped?

00:43:49.927 --> 00:43:52.054 line:80%
There you go with that nagging again.

00:43:53.013 --> 00:43:55.433 line:80%
I swear I'm perfectly fine.

00:43:55.516 --> 00:43:56.892 line:80%
Stop worrying for no reason.

00:44:01.313 --> 00:44:02.356 line:80%
[sighs]

00:44:02.440 --> 00:44:05.067 line:80%
[♪ pop music playing]

00:44:05.901 --> 00:44:06.902 line:80%
[sighs]

00:44:08.946 --> 00:44:09.822 line:80%
Oh…

00:44:09.905 --> 00:44:11.657 line:80%
-[Hyejeong] <i>Hello? Ms. Seong?</i>
-Hey. I'm here.

00:44:12.658 --> 00:44:13.826 line:80%
Yeah.

00:44:14.493 --> 00:44:15.703 line:80%
<i>Are you okay?</i>

00:44:15.786 --> 00:44:17.705 line:80%
Yeah, so nice. I mean, it's fine.

00:44:18.581 --> 00:44:19.623 line:80%
See you tomorrow.

00:44:24.086 --> 00:44:26.005 line:80%
It's our first night as a married couple.

00:44:35.639 --> 00:44:36.724 line:80%
Are you ready?

00:44:50.821 --> 00:44:53.032 line:80%
[machine beeping]

00:44:57.745 --> 00:44:58.871 line:80%
[Hyeon] No way.

00:44:58.954 --> 00:45:02.082 line:80%
I'm sure no one knows their way
around the palace better than me.

00:45:02.958 --> 00:45:05.461 line:80%
That only shows you the main pathways.

00:45:05.544 --> 00:45:07.171 line:80%
If you want to follow that,

00:45:07.254 --> 00:45:09.298 line:80%
you should be prepared
to walk 12,000 steps.

00:45:09.798 --> 00:45:10.799 line:80%
Are you sure?

00:45:10.883 --> 00:45:12.218 line:80%
You should trust me.

00:45:12.301 --> 00:45:13.594 line:80%
If you go this way,

00:45:13.677 --> 00:45:15.346 line:80%
you'll be in your room in ten minutes.

00:45:20.100 --> 00:45:22.603 line:80%
When did you start working at the palace?

00:45:23.938 --> 00:45:25.022 line:80%
What?

00:45:25.105 --> 00:45:27.816 line:80%
I mean, you're still pretty young.

00:45:28.317 --> 00:45:30.444 line:80%
But you know everything,
like you were born here.

00:45:30.528 --> 00:45:31.987 line:80%
From the staff to the pathways.

00:45:33.447 --> 00:45:37.034 line:80%
I'm not exactly sure.
I think I was five or six?

00:45:37.868 --> 00:45:38.869 line:80%
What?

00:45:39.370 --> 00:45:40.704 line:80%
I'm an orphan, you see.

00:45:41.997 --> 00:45:44.542 line:80%
I heard I was abandoned
in front of the private residence.

00:45:46.544 --> 00:45:49.046 line:80%
[whimpers] Sorry.

00:45:49.880 --> 00:45:50.881 line:80%
Pardon?

00:45:50.965 --> 00:45:54.134 line:80%
I shouldn't have asked. Right?

00:45:54.718 --> 00:45:56.512 line:80%
Oh! No, it's perfectly fine.

00:45:56.595 --> 00:45:57.888 line:80%
You see,

00:45:58.430 --> 00:46:01.809 line:80%
I'm really grateful to my parents.

00:46:02.393 --> 00:46:05.312 line:80%
I grew up surrounded by love
at the private residence.

00:46:05.396 --> 00:46:07.940 line:80%
Of all places, I just happened
to be abandoned right in front

00:46:08.023 --> 00:46:09.775 line:80%
of the Grand Prince's house.

00:46:10.526 --> 00:46:13.529 line:80%
You could say
I'm sort of a "lucky guy." [laughs]

00:46:13.612 --> 00:46:15.614 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:46:24.498 --> 00:46:26.792 line:80%
[heartbeat thumping]

00:46:33.173 --> 00:46:35.843 line:80%
What are you doing?
We need to make it in 10 minutes.

00:46:35.926 --> 00:46:36.927 line:80%
Right.

00:46:39.221 --> 00:46:40.222 line:80%
What's wrong with you?

00:46:51.483 --> 00:46:53.319 line:80%
[machine beeping]

00:46:53.402 --> 00:46:54.403 line:80%
[sighs]

00:46:57.406 --> 00:46:58.616 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:47:01.327 --> 00:47:04.496 line:80%
Will you not even consider the sofa?

00:47:04.580 --> 00:47:05.581 line:80%
[I-AN] No.

00:47:06.248 --> 00:47:07.708 line:80%
This is perfectly fine.

00:47:08.500 --> 00:47:10.210 line:80%
The sofa would be perfectly fine too.

00:47:11.003 --> 00:47:12.212 line:80%
Then you should go.

00:47:13.297 --> 00:47:14.590 line:80%
That'd be perfect.

00:47:17.968 --> 00:47:19.178 line:80%
I'm the patient here.

00:47:20.638 --> 00:47:22.181 line:80%
[I-AN mumbles]

00:47:22.264 --> 00:47:23.265 line:80%
[sighs]

00:47:29.897 --> 00:47:31.315 line:80%
Seriously?

00:47:34.777 --> 00:47:36.070 line:80%
Just sleep already.

00:47:36.153 --> 00:47:38.697 line:80%
Want everyone to think
I was cast aside on our first night?

00:47:41.158 --> 00:47:43.494 line:80%
[machine beeping]

00:47:51.752 --> 00:47:53.170 line:80%
[sighs]

00:48:05.391 --> 00:48:07.059 line:80%
Should we turn that off?

00:48:10.854 --> 00:48:11.855 line:80%
Just leave it.

00:48:11.939 --> 00:48:13.148 line:80%
[sighs]

00:48:14.149 --> 00:48:15.651 line:80%
But it's so loud.

00:48:17.277 --> 00:48:19.029 line:80%
It's proof you're alive.

00:48:20.989 --> 00:48:23.325 line:80%
[♪ soft pop playing]

00:48:27.162 --> 00:48:28.163 line:80%
I like the sound of it.

00:48:46.306 --> 00:48:47.641 line:80%
I'm just reassuring you.

00:48:49.601 --> 00:48:51.103 line:80%
I'm right here.

00:49:06.034 --> 00:49:07.453 line:80%
[sighs]

00:49:50.204 --> 00:49:52.956 line:80%
Both her blood pressure
and pulse are stable.

00:49:53.040 --> 00:49:54.082 line:80%
[Lady Choi] Thank you.

00:49:55.250 --> 00:49:56.251 line:80%
Ms. Do--

00:49:57.002 --> 00:49:58.003 line:80%
Aide Do!

00:49:58.796 --> 00:49:59.838 line:80%
[Hyeon] Yes?

00:50:04.968 --> 00:50:06.386 line:80%
I didn't call for you.

00:50:06.470 --> 00:50:09.973 line:80%
I know, but you should ask for me
for the time being.

00:50:10.057 --> 00:50:12.851 line:80%
I will be the chief aide
of the Grand Princess for now.

00:50:12.935 --> 00:50:14.102 line:80%
-Why?
-Mmm,

00:50:14.186 --> 00:50:16.355 line:80%
because you'll need
an experienced aide

00:50:16.438 --> 00:50:19.149 line:80%
well-versed in royal duties by your side

00:50:19.233 --> 00:50:20.859 line:80%
to facilitate your swift transition.

00:50:20.943 --> 00:50:23.111 line:80%
Th-Then what about my Ms. Do?

00:50:23.195 --> 00:50:24.363 line:80%
Where is my Hyejeong?

00:50:25.239 --> 00:50:27.407 line:80%
-What did you do with her?
-She's safe.

00:50:27.491 --> 00:50:28.659 line:80%
Hyejeong!

00:50:28.742 --> 00:50:31.912 line:80%
It's a Royal Academy event,
so security shouldn't be a major issue.

00:50:31.995 --> 00:50:34.832 line:80%
It's a small-scale event
that will be held indoors.

00:50:34.915 --> 00:50:36.124 line:80%
[I-AN clears throat]

00:50:38.418 --> 00:50:41.213 line:80%
You should be familiar
with most of the guests.

00:50:41.296 --> 00:50:42.673 line:80%
They're all former students.

00:50:56.019 --> 00:50:57.646 line:80%
Anyone I should be mindful of?

00:50:58.397 --> 00:50:59.523 line:80%
Prime Minister Min Jeongwoo.

00:50:59.606 --> 00:51:01.400 line:80%
He is set to deliver the opening address.

00:51:01.483 --> 00:51:03.610 line:80%
Your Royal Highness
will present the scholarship.

00:51:08.115 --> 00:51:09.116 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:51:13.704 --> 00:51:16.707 line:80%
There are a few protocols
you must follow during official duties.

00:51:16.790 --> 00:51:19.835 line:80%
First, you must never walk
ahead of His Royal Highness.

00:51:19.918 --> 00:51:23.714 line:80%
Hold on. This was something I mentioned
for the Inner Court Banquet as well.

00:51:24.256 --> 00:51:26.550 line:80%
Court rank is very important
in official events.

00:51:26.633 --> 00:51:28.719 line:80%
I understand.

00:51:29.386 --> 00:51:30.846 line:80%
Yes. Thank you. [clears throat]

00:51:30.929 --> 00:51:33.807 line:80%
You will sometimes come across
people who hand you flowers or letters.

00:51:33.891 --> 00:51:35.142 line:80%
You should accept all of them.

00:51:35.225 --> 00:51:36.894 line:80%
-All of them?
-Yes, all of them.

00:51:36.977 --> 00:51:39.271 line:80%
And your photo could be taken at any time.

00:51:39.354 --> 00:51:40.814 line:80%
So try not to appear

00:51:40.898 --> 00:51:43.275 line:80%
expressionless or put on that face
you just gave me.

00:51:43.358 --> 00:51:45.110 line:80%
There you go again.

00:51:45.193 --> 00:51:46.737 line:80%
You cannot do that.

00:51:47.321 --> 00:51:51.241 line:80%
Also, you must observe rank when offering
a handshake or initiating a conversation.

00:51:51.325 --> 00:51:54.244 line:80%
His Royal Highness is first.
You come second.

00:51:54.328 --> 00:51:57.205 line:80%
Does that mean no one can speak to me
if I don't speak to them first?

00:51:57.289 --> 00:51:58.373 line:80%
Correct.

00:51:58.457 --> 00:52:00.334 line:80%
And you can never show bare feet.

00:52:00.417 --> 00:52:03.378 line:80%
If there are no slippers available,
please keep your shoes on.

00:52:03.462 --> 00:52:06.423 line:80%
Crossing your legs while seated
is strictly forbidden,

00:52:06.506 --> 00:52:07.591 line:80%
so please be careful.

00:52:07.674 --> 00:52:10.802 line:80%
No peace signs or finger hearts
when being photographed.

00:52:10.886 --> 00:52:12.679 line:80%
Cheek hearts? Definitely not.

00:52:13.180 --> 00:52:15.307 line:80%
Then what exactly am I supposed to do?

00:52:15.390 --> 00:52:16.975 line:80%
Something simple.

00:52:17.935 --> 00:52:19.519 line:80%
Maybe a simple wave?

00:52:19.603 --> 00:52:20.687 line:80%
[sighs]

00:52:22.189 --> 00:52:23.315 line:80%
Ah…

00:52:24.608 --> 00:52:26.735 line:80%
I should wear this one today.

00:52:26.818 --> 00:52:29.655 line:80%
I should do my part to boost
our affiliate's revenue again.

00:52:30.489 --> 00:52:31.698 line:80%
What do you think?

00:52:31.782 --> 00:52:32.950 line:80%
[in English] Good choice.

00:52:34.618 --> 00:52:36.161 line:80%
[in Korean] So pretty. Hmm.

00:52:38.330 --> 00:52:39.873 line:80%
Ready to go?

00:52:39.957 --> 00:52:41.166 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:52:42.459 --> 00:52:43.877 line:80%
I will be after you change.

00:52:45.629 --> 00:52:47.798 line:80%
Why? Do I look weird?

00:52:48.632 --> 00:52:51.301 line:80%
It's our first official appearance
as a married couple.

00:52:51.385 --> 00:52:53.845 line:80%
Our outfits should look coordinated.

00:52:53.929 --> 00:52:56.807 line:80%
[clicks tongue]
Such a gloomy outfit. Right?

00:52:56.890 --> 00:52:58.350 line:80%
-My thoughts exactly.
-Mmm.

00:53:00.060 --> 00:53:01.311 line:80%
-Just look at it.
-[gasps]

00:53:01.395 --> 00:53:02.771 line:80%
[in English] So shiny!

00:53:02.854 --> 00:53:03.939 line:80%
Wow.

00:53:04.439 --> 00:53:06.483 line:80%
[in Korean]
We must leave a record of this. Right?

00:53:06.566 --> 00:53:08.360 line:80%
All right now. Here we go.

00:53:08.443 --> 00:53:09.778 line:80%
Look right over here.

00:53:10.278 --> 00:53:12.030 line:80%
-Let's try smiling.
-[giggling]

00:53:12.114 --> 00:53:13.573 line:80%
Oh, my gosh.

00:53:13.657 --> 00:53:15.075 line:80%
-Oh, my goodness.
-[Huiju] Shall we?

00:53:15.659 --> 00:53:16.952 line:80%
Shall we take this to the hallway?

00:53:17.035 --> 00:53:19.037 line:80%
Come on now. Here we go.

00:53:20.622 --> 00:53:22.124 line:80%
Does it look gloomy?

00:53:22.207 --> 00:53:24.835 line:80%
Absolutely not.
You look so cool right now.

00:53:24.918 --> 00:53:25.919 line:80%
"Gloomy"?

00:53:26.003 --> 00:53:28.797 line:80%
[scoffs] How could she say that
to the world's most handsome man?

00:53:34.469 --> 00:53:36.513 line:80%
-Sir.
-I was actually just on my way out.

00:53:36.596 --> 00:53:38.015 line:80%
You need to take a look at this.

00:53:48.984 --> 00:53:51.403 line:80%
Criticism of the Crown
will be unavoidable.

00:53:51.486 --> 00:53:52.446 line:80%
What do you think?

00:53:55.115 --> 00:53:56.283 line:80%
[breathes shakily]

00:53:58.243 --> 00:54:00.787 line:80%
[♪ upbeat music playing]

00:54:07.836 --> 00:54:11.006 line:80%
[crowd cheering]

00:54:33.153 --> 00:54:34.529 line:80%
Aren't we going inside?

00:54:35.572 --> 00:54:36.990 line:80%
Enough of that. Take my arm.

00:54:38.116 --> 00:54:39.910 line:80%
Why? I'm busy being loved.

00:54:39.993 --> 00:54:42.621 line:80%
[chuckles] Go on without me.

00:54:49.836 --> 00:54:51.004 line:80%
They look so affectionate.

00:54:51.505 --> 00:54:52.506 line:80%
I know, right?

00:54:56.426 --> 00:54:57.427 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:55:14.694 --> 00:55:17.155 line:80%
[Hyeon] I made it so crystal clear

00:55:17.239 --> 00:55:19.825 line:80%
that you can't do these finger hearts…
[laughs]

00:55:19.908 --> 00:55:21.243 line:80%
Please stop that.

00:55:21.326 --> 00:55:22.869 line:80%
Come on now.

00:55:22.953 --> 00:55:24.579 line:80%
P-Please stop, Your Royal Highness.

00:55:25.372 --> 00:55:26.581 line:80%
[Hyejeong] Yes, sure.

00:55:27.082 --> 00:55:28.125 line:80%
Thank you.

00:55:28.208 --> 00:55:29.626 line:80%
[call end tone]

00:55:29.709 --> 00:55:32.212 line:80%
Your Royal Highness,
that was the prime minister's office.

00:55:32.295 --> 00:55:33.672 line:80%
He's going to be a little late.

00:55:33.755 --> 00:55:35.090 line:80%
-Really?
-Jeongwoo is?

00:55:35.757 --> 00:55:36.758 line:80%
Can you…

00:55:37.467 --> 00:55:39.511 line:80%
stop addressing him like that?

00:55:41.638 --> 00:55:43.431 line:80%
I'm not supposed to call him by his name?

00:55:43.515 --> 00:55:46.810 line:80%
-"Prime Minister Min."
-[Hyejeong] You should first review this.

00:55:47.394 --> 00:55:48.645 line:80%
Why?

00:55:48.728 --> 00:55:50.272 line:80%
They sent over the opening address.

00:55:50.772 --> 00:55:52.566 line:80%
Since he is presenting the scholarships,

00:55:52.649 --> 00:55:55.402 line:80%
wouldn't it be nice
if you delivered the opening address?

00:55:57.279 --> 00:56:00.699 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:56:00.782 --> 00:56:02.117 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:56:03.618 --> 00:56:06.121 line:80%
[cheering]

00:56:12.919 --> 00:56:14.963 line:80%
Hello, I am Seong Huiju.

00:56:20.427 --> 00:56:22.179 line:80%
Being back at my alma mater,

00:56:22.762 --> 00:56:25.056 line:80%
I feel like I should be
introducing myself by saying,

00:56:25.140 --> 00:56:26.808 line:80%
"I am Seong Huiju of Jujak House."

00:56:28.143 --> 00:56:30.937 line:80%
Another part of me wants to celebrate
my success since graduating

00:56:32.022 --> 00:56:34.274 line:80%
by presenting myself
as Seong Huiju, the Executive Director

00:56:34.858 --> 00:56:36.276 line:80%
of Castle Group.

00:56:37.485 --> 00:56:41.114 line:80%
However, I am sure
all of you would most like to hear,

00:56:42.949 --> 00:56:43.992 line:80%
"Hello,

00:56:44.826 --> 00:56:46.494 line:80%
I am Grand Princess Seong Huiju."

00:56:48.330 --> 00:56:49.456 line:80%
Am I right?

00:56:49.539 --> 00:56:52.918 line:80%
[crowd laughing]

00:56:55.587 --> 00:56:57.255 line:80%
-[laughs]
-She's unbelievable.

00:56:59.382 --> 00:57:01.259 line:80%
-She's so good, isn't she?
-[phone buzzing]

00:57:03.094 --> 00:57:04.304 line:80%
[sighs]

00:57:05.138 --> 00:57:07.724 line:80%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:57:21.613 --> 00:57:22.864 line:80%
[Huiju] Eighty years ago,

00:57:23.448 --> 00:57:25.450 line:80%
when the Royal Academy was founded,

00:57:25.533 --> 00:57:28.495 line:80%
the Crown pursued but one ideal.

00:57:29.454 --> 00:57:32.540 line:80%
Any who aspired to become something

00:57:33.458 --> 00:57:34.793 line:80%
shall be allowed to do so,

00:57:35.418 --> 00:57:37.754 line:80%
without regard to background

00:57:38.463 --> 00:57:39.756 line:80%
or gender.

00:57:39.839 --> 00:57:43.343 line:80%
I, too, was a beneficiary of that mission,

00:57:44.386 --> 00:57:45.553 line:80%
and as you can see,

00:57:46.137 --> 00:57:50.016 line:80%
I managed to make
all my aspirations a reality.

00:57:50.100 --> 00:57:52.560 line:80%
[crowd laughing]

00:57:52.644 --> 00:57:53.687 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:57:59.609 --> 00:58:02.696 line:80%
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

00:58:02.779 --> 00:58:05.699 line:80%
A PERSON OF VIRTUE
TAKES RIGHTEOUSNESS…

00:58:05.782 --> 00:58:07.200 line:80%
TAKEN AS FOUNDATION

00:58:12.080 --> 00:58:13.498 line:80%
There is an emergency, Your Majesty.

00:58:14.749 --> 00:58:16.209 line:80%
What is it?

00:58:16.293 --> 00:58:18.878 line:80%
If there is something that you want,

00:58:19.879 --> 00:58:20.880 line:80%
do not hesitate…

00:58:20.964 --> 00:58:23.091 line:80%
-[phones buzzing]
-…and claim it for yourself.

00:58:25.552 --> 00:58:27.971 line:80%
As your senior alum and patron,

00:58:28.847 --> 00:58:31.182 line:80%
with ironclad resolve…

00:58:31.891 --> 00:58:34.019 line:80%
-[crowd murmuring]
-[clears throat]

00:58:38.315 --> 00:58:40.400 line:80%
With ironclad resolve…

00:58:41.401 --> 00:58:43.403 line:80%
-[door opens]
-[reporters clamoring]

00:58:45.280 --> 00:58:47.782 line:80%
[reporter 1] Your Royal Highness!

00:58:47.866 --> 00:58:50.535 line:80%
Do you have anything to say for yourself?

00:58:50.618 --> 00:58:52.245 line:80%
[reporter 2] Did you deceive the people?

00:58:52.329 --> 00:58:54.873 line:80%
[reporter 3] There was a confidentiality
clause. What are you hiding?

00:58:56.207 --> 00:58:58.668 line:80%
EXCLUSIVE: THE ROYAL COUPLE'S
MARRIAGE CONTRACT LEAKED

00:58:58.752 --> 00:59:02.005 line:80%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:59:02.088 --> 00:59:04.341 line:80%
[reporter 4] Is it true that that
the marriage is contractual?

00:59:04.424 --> 00:59:06.968 line:80%
[reporter 5] Is it true
you plan to divorce in three years?

00:59:07.052 --> 00:59:08.345 line:80%
Please respond!

00:59:15.226 --> 00:59:16.770 line:80%
Was there consent from the royal family?

00:59:16.853 --> 00:59:19.064 line:80%
What has Castle Group promised the Crown?

00:59:29.574 --> 00:59:32.202 line:80%
[clamoring fades]

00:59:43.546 --> 00:59:45.715 line:80%
[clamoring]

00:59:48.968 --> 00:59:50.220 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:59:52.472 --> 00:59:53.473 line:80%
Keep your eyes on me.

00:59:53.556 --> 00:59:54.474 line:80%
[clamoring fades]

00:59:54.557 --> 00:59:57.894 line:80%
[♪ soft pop playing]

01:00:12.283 --> 01:00:14.285 line:80%
[reporters clamoring]

01:00:16.496 --> 01:00:18.164 line:80%
[clamoring fades]

01:00:27.757 --> 01:00:30.677 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

01:01:06.713 --> 01:01:09.090 line:80%
[reporter] Is it true that
the marriage is contractual?

01:01:09.174 --> 01:01:10.800 line:80%
[Hyeon] <i>This is about to blow up</i>
<i>in our face.</i>

01:01:10.884 --> 01:01:14.387 line:80%
[Yun] <i>You thought you could protect</i>
<i>yourself with that measly contract?</i>

01:01:14.971 --> 01:01:17.182 line:80%
I shall set the record straight myself.

01:01:17.265 --> 01:01:19.184 line:80%
Can Your Majesty prove it?

01:01:19.267 --> 01:01:21.269 line:80%
Do you think I'm oblivious
to your scheming?

01:01:21.352 --> 01:01:22.353 line:80%
Your Royal Highness!

01:01:23.354 --> 01:01:24.772 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] <i>You said it was all for show.</i>

01:01:24.856 --> 01:01:26.232 line:20%
<i>You and the Grand Prince.</i>

01:01:27.150 --> 01:01:28.318 line:20%
[Huiju] <i>I like him.</i>

01:01:28.818 --> 01:01:29.903 line:20%
<i>A lot.</i>

01:01:31.070 --> 01:01:31.988 line:20%
HUIJU

01:01:32.071 --> 01:01:33.823 line:20%
[Jeongwoo]
<i>His Royal Highness remains unaware.</i>

01:01:33.907 --> 01:01:35.158 line:20%
[Yun] <i>How does it feel?</i>

01:01:35.241 --> 01:01:36.659 line:20%
[Huiju] <i>What do I have to do?</i>

01:01:38.328 --> 01:01:39.329 line:20%
[I-AN] <i>Are you scared?</i>

01:01:40.246 --> 01:01:42.457 line:20%
[Huiju] <i>I'm scared I might end up</i>

01:01:42.540 --> 01:01:43.583 line:20%
<i>ruining you.</i>

01:01:49.631 --> 01:01:53.843 line:20%
EPILOGUE

01:01:53.927 --> 01:01:56.638 line:20%
[machine beeping]

01:01:57.305 --> 01:01:59.432 line:20%
[♪ uplifting music playing]

01:02:04.521 --> 01:02:07.315 line:20%
Your Royal Highness,
it is Court Lady Choi.

01:02:07.398 --> 01:02:08.942 line:20%
[Huiju mumbles]

01:02:09.025 --> 01:02:10.485 line:20%
[Lady Choi] Your Royal Highness.

01:02:11.152 --> 01:02:12.570 line:20%
[groans]

01:02:13.655 --> 01:02:14.948 line:20%
[Lady Choi] Your Royal Highness!

01:02:24.290 --> 01:02:25.959 line:20%
Are you awake?

01:02:28.211 --> 01:02:29.546 line:20%
[sighs]

01:02:29.629 --> 01:02:31.422 line:20%
-Should I just go in there?
-[phone buzzes]

01:02:31.506 --> 01:02:32.799 line:20%
Would that be okay?

01:02:33.299 --> 01:02:34.676 line:20%
IF YOU WAKE UP
THE GRAND PRINCESS…

01:02:34.759 --> 01:02:35.843 line:20%
-Your Royal High--
-Stop.

01:02:37.428 --> 01:02:39.138 line:20%
He says to keep it down.

01:02:39.931 --> 01:02:41.015 line:20%
Pardon me?

01:02:41.099 --> 01:02:43.184 line:20%
He says if we wake
the Grand Princess… [sucks teeth]

01:02:43.268 --> 01:02:44.561 line:20%
…there will be hell to pay.

01:02:45.603 --> 01:02:46.646 line:20%
[chuckles]

01:02:48.940 --> 01:02:51.234 line:20%
-Should we go get some breakfast?
-Shall we?

01:02:52.777 --> 01:02:53.820 line:20%
What are you craving?

01:02:53.903 --> 01:02:56.322 line:20%
There's a place with amazing pajeon
right by here.

01:03:36.696 --> 01:03:38.698 line:20%
Translated by Justin S. Kim

01:03:50.001 --> 01:03:53.713 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN